<item>
            <title>[LU-15964] rpmbuild: Correctly handle CONFIGURE_ARGS</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-15964</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Currently multiple arguments passed through rpmbuild as&lt;br/&gt;
CONFIGURE_ARGS are interpreted as a single argument.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Ex rpmbuild argument:&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160;-&lt;del&gt;define &quot;configure_args &apos;&lt;/del&gt;-with-o2ib=... --arg2 --arg3&apos;&quot;&lt;br/&gt;
is interpreted as:&lt;br/&gt;
&#160; &#160;./configure --with-o2ib=&apos;... --arg2 --arg3&apos;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;effectively discarding --arg2 and --arg3.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The contents of CONFIGURE_ARGS should have the quotes removed&lt;br/&gt;
before being forwarded to configure&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="70848">LU-15964</key>
