                            <comment id="338512" author="stancheff" created="Thu, 23 Jun 2022 14:43:52 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User error. Not a bug.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="338511" author="stancheff" created="Thu, 23 Jun 2022 14:43:03 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;User error, correct use of configure_args is to separate each argument with single quotes Ex:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;rpmbuild --rebuild --with zfs --define &quot;zfs 5&quot; --without mpi \
    --define &quot;configure_args &apos;--with-o2ib=/usr/src/ofa_kernel/default\&apos; \&apos;--disable-dlc\&apos; \&apos;--disable-gss-keyring\&apos; \&apos;--enable-gss=no&apos;&quot; \
    --define &quot;lustre_name lustre_ib&quot; ${HOME}/lustre-release/*.src.rpm
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&#160;&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
